metadata.name: was not something the new
metadata.description:
could overcome.



As Nestum hurried toward the BLUE POND with anxiety, the sound of gold iron CROSSING the BLUE pond gradually fell, and in the cold winter, a touch of red was particularly conspicuous in the snow.



To one side.



A middle-aged man stood tall.



He was dressed in black, with a sword in his right hand. The sword was not drawn, but his eyes were staring straight ahead, serious and angry.
